_sText:
My fully usable M1A1 Abrams Tank. Hop in, and drive by pressing the button. To switch to the turret mod, right click, and right click again to get back to driving. As anyone whos ever used a CSS vehicle before would know, to get out, jump, crouch, hit E, and swear alot. :P If you use this in your map, please credit me for the tank! And also, I'd like to know what maps its in :P
“Patriots always talk of dying for their country and never of killing for their country.”Bertrand Russell (1872-05-18— 1970-02-02)
